cs.MM, cs.IR, cs.NI, cs.SI, cs.HC 

The paper discusses QoS-aware recommendations for multimedia services/applications, which suggests that it could fall under the categories of Multimedia (cs.MM), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Networked and Distributed Systems (cs.NI), Social and Information Networks (cs.SI), and Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC). The paper focuses on improving user experience and retention rates, which aligns with the goals of these categories.
